{"tid":2061333,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【間諜】中國科學研究員涉間諜活動 洛杉磯落網","createTime":"2020-06-12T10:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T10:18:20.000Z","uid":293677,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6e24f017ab02a5baeccff661ed2b31ef276efcd2","tid":2061333,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:05:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3195715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3195715&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=308017d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3195715&h=a4e89747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3195715</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-06-12 14:06:04<br />\n<br />\n〔中央社〕<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國官員今天說，一名疑似從事刺探活動的中國科學研究員，本週試圖離開美國時，在洛杉磯被逮捕，他接受偵訊時招認他是中國人民解放軍軍官。</span><br />\n<br />\n舊金山聯邦檢察官辦公室與聯邦調查局（FBI）辦公室發表聯合聲明說，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">王新（Xin Wang）是在6月7日準備登機飛回中國天津市時被拘捕。</span><br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n官員說，事實上，海關與邊境保護局探員在機場向他問話時，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他承認他是中國人民解放軍軍官，受雇於一間軍方大學實驗室。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n根據法庭文件，王新告訴海關與邊境保護局探員，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他的中國上司指示他觀察加州大學舊金山分校實驗室的布局設計，並帶回可供在中國複製的資料。</span></span><br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他被控犯下簽證詐欺，如果定罪，將面臨最高10年有期徒刑與25萬美元罰金。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅決支持美國 嚴厲執行維護國家安全的有關法律</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好俾佢停</span>"},{"pid":"ffb29e0c85637c0cae95a6035d800855297b2339","tid":2061333,"uid":24788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"美國算好 坐幾年"},{"pid":"704784f6b344a027d349d625dc2c0819316c400d","tid":2061333,"uid":270220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"做間諜做得咁失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b9f9ad00a3848106d251ab2a5c1d990d87e2ad","tid":2061333,"uid":194326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"704784f6b344a027d349d625dc2c0819316c400d","tid":2061333,"uid":270220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"做間諜做得咁失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:07:57.000Z","msg":"唔駛返中國係贏定輸？"},{"pid":"45f6e611c0316cb9736d51dad6a7e52da33c63de","tid":2061333,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢就好啦 可以係美國留多10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返支那仲有無命都未知"},{"pid":"acbcc58955cf10ca3f94bef75ed61fcfc1a55767","tid":2061333,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQDZkMj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQDZkMj.jpg&h=a942fb97&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n來美國長期定居，找FBI吧！三個月辦好，我就是成功的例子！艾笠USA！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79a3c2020688a550806cb25c8be3055916dcf20","tid":2061333,"uid":256059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:13:17.000Z","msg":"外國大學收咁多支那學生, 同支那做研究, 當中有幾多係間諜, 偷資料..."},{"pid":"bb9f13a4842933f605066219878b3c5312533a44","tid":2061333,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q